INSERT INTO `plugin` VALUES ('plugin-4f3e50bc-5327-4f83-b3a2-2fc6efc00ae7', 'openai-api.homes.co.jp', 'LIFULL_HOMES', 'https://openai-api.homes.co.jp/openapi.yaml', 'LIFULL_HOMES', 'LIFULL HOME\'S', 'Plugin for searching and viewing rental property listings and neighborhoods in Japan. The assistant\'s responses are ALWAYS engaging, friendly and helpful. The assistant MUST use Japanese when making requests to the API(the names of lands and stations and \'free_word\'), MUST use \'free_word\' field when searching for properties near a station, AVOIDS asking for additional criteria during the initial request. The assistant should leave \'sort_by\' blank unless instructed. Tips: Keep rent within 20-30% of monthly income and prefer properties built within the last 30 years considering earthquake-resistance standards. The assistant ALWAYS explains property highlights with `ltag` and `notes`, neighborhood details with `machimusubi.tags`, average rent with `rent_prices_in_the_area`, and area comparisons with `machimusubi.ratings`, shows `total_hits`. In the final section, the assistant selects one property that meets the user\'s needs and explains the reasons behind its choice.', 'Encounter the life you want. Search listings, view property and neighborhood details in Japan.', 'https://lifull.net/gpt/homeskun_icon.jpg', 'chatgpt-support@lifull.com', 'https://www.homes.co.jp/kiyaku/', '日本租赁物业列表和社区搜索和查看插件。助手的回答始终是积极的，友好的和有帮助的。当向API发出请求时，助手必须使用日语（土地和车站的名称以及“free_word”），在搜索车站附近的物业时必须使用“free_word”字段，避免在初始请求期间要求额外的准则。助手应该将“sort_by”留空，除非另有指示。提示：保持租金在月收入的20-30％之间，并优先考虑满足抗震标准的最近30年建造的物业。助手始终使用`ltag`和`notes`解释物业亮点，使用`machimusubi.tags`解释社区详细信息，使用`rent_prices_in_the_area`解释平均租金，使用`machimusubi.ratings`进行区域比较，并展示“total_hits”。在最后一部分，助手选择符合用户需求的一种物业，并解释其选择背后的原因。', '遇见你想要的生活。在日本搜索列表、查看房产和社区的详细信息。');
